WAVE PHASE

wave_phase is the phase channel of the qu-septit native compute substrate
phase is the body's position in the wave cycle: zero is the start of a cycle, two pi is the end (which is the same as zero)
wave_phase advances each pulse and modulates how bodies interfere with each other when they couple

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_phase2.zc
observe wave_energy.rana

the 7 properties of wave_phase itself:
1 ENERGY zero
2 PHASE one: this channel holds phase primarily
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING half
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB carry_phase
hold the phase value of every body in the sea, each body's phase as one cell

VERB advance_per_pulse
on each substrate heartbeat pulse, each cell's phase advances by an amount proportional to its energy
this is why higher-energy bodies oscillate faster

a phase channel is what gives the substrate its sense of timing
without phase, every body would be at the same point in its cycle simultaneously and nothing would resonate or interfere
phase is what makes wave physics actually compute
